To fill bytes bytes: buffer of 4 u8 with value: u8.
Let i be 0.
While i is less than 4: bytes at i becomes value; i becomes i plus 1.

To sum bytes bytes: buffer of 4 u8, giving i32.
Let total be 0.
Let i be 0.
While i is less than 4: total becomes total plus (bytes at i as i32); i becomes i plus 1.
Give total.

To main, giving i32.
Let bytes be buffer of 4 u8 filled with 0.
fill bytes bytes with 9.
Give sum bytes bytes.
